  • Constructor Details

    • CPSequenceVarImpl

      public CPSequenceVarImpl(CPSolver cp, int nNodes, int begin, int end)
      Creates a Sequence Variable, representing a path from begin until end in a complete insertion graph. At the construction the sequence only contains the begin and end nodes.
      Parameters:
      cp - solver related to the variable.
      nNodes - >= 2 is number of nodes in the graph
      begin - first node of the path, must be a node of the graph, thus in the range [0..nNodes-1]
      end - last node of the path, must be a node of the graph, different than begin.
